membership:
IIOC is an Associate member of the International Accreditation Forum www.iaf.nu - the global organisation for accreditation bodies. IIOC is highly active within IAF representing its members on a range of committees, working groups, task forces, etc.&#xd;
&#xd;
IIOC is a recognized stakeholder of European Accreditation https://www.european-accreditation.org and contributes to a number of EA committees.&#xd;
&#xd;
IIOC has liaison to a number of the International Organization for Standardization www.iso.org, assisting in the development of key standards which IIOC members audit against and standards which describe who this auditing is done.
